site_name: Land At London Road Car Park And Site Adjacent Valetta Grove
description: Demolition of existing buildings and redevelopment of the London Road site to provide buildings of 2-23 storeys providing 100 residential units and retail (Use Classes A1/A2/A3) and gym (Use Class D2), and redevelopment of the Valetta Grove site to provide a building of 6-15 storeys providing 82 residential units and a neighbourhood centre (Use Class D1) along with landscaping, car and cycle parking and associated works.
site_number: Land At London Road Car Park And Site Adjacent Valetta Grove
